This stunning heart-shaped necklace features a stylish cutout design at the bottom of the heart. The word ""Mom"" is written with a heart for the ""O,"" adding a unique touch. Up to three names or a special message can be engraved on the surface of the heart to create a truly one-of-a-kind piece. It makes the perfect gift for Mother's day, her birthday, a special occasion or just because!

Create a beautiful and personalized piece that is uniquely yours. Engrave your name or any text that is meaningful to you. Choose from a selection of fonts, each creating a statement of its own. Make a name necklace as individual as you are today!

Each necklace is made from solid precious metal (never plated). Choose from .925 sterling silver, or 10K or 14K gold, offered in white, yellow, or rose. The chain is made of the same metal as your necklace, with your choice of either 16¡± or 18¡± in length, fastened with a spring ring clasp.

Every Jewlr item is designed and manufactured in the United States and Canada. Staying local means we can maintain quality control for every product, minimize costs to our customers, and ensure a quick turnaround time - so you can receive your beautiful, handcrafted piece as soon as possible.

Every order is delivered in our sleek and elegant custom packaging. At checkout, you also have the option of further personalizing the packaging of your item. We offer a selection of wrapping paper and gift envelopes. Every Jewlr purchase includes the Certificate of Authenticity, and you can write a personalized message to be sent along with your gift. Customize an order with us to create beautiful jewelry that comes ready to gift!

simple,,"100% Cashmere Scarf - Multiple Colors, Gift Boxed, Premium Quality",1,0,visible,,"

Cashmere is a very rare type of wool that is much softer, lighter, and warmer than regular wool. Cashmere comes from a special breed of goats that live at a high altitude and in an extremely cold climate. To stay warm, the goats create a downy undercoat of cashmere to be a barrier against the cold.Cashmere is a thin layer of inner down, while wool is the thick course outer layer. Because cashmere is on the inside it is not exposed to the elements, dirt, and other contaminates.Cashmere wool is 6x finer than human hair. So it has super insulation properties. The millions of ultra-fine fibers trap pockets of air in between them, which prevents warm air from your body from escaping and stops cold air entering. Because cashmere is so fine it offers superior insulation without weighing a lot.Cashmere is extremely rare. Each goat produces only .3lbs of cashmere per year. It is much harder to obtain, process, and weave than wool, which is why we sell a limited amount of scarfs. How to tie a hair scarf
Put the middle point over your forehead, between your eyes and tie the other two ends into knot above it.
Fold the point over toward the back of your head and tuck it into the knot.
Secure it by tying the two ends into another knot and tucking them into the sides of the scarf.
Fold your scarf lengthwise a few times and put the center of it just above your hairline.
Tie it at the nape of your neck. The knot should be under your hair.
